{"tid":842281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被拒訪港後美「黃蜂號」赴南海演習   甲板上陸戰隊裝甲車進行實彈射擊","createTime":"2018-09-30T07:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T00:51:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"37d690ac9abfd5fd0cf3c5463c6ef108d40e5661","tid":842281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180930/large/1538281695_7613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180930%2Flarge%2F1538281695_7613.jpg&h=a222c62e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國日前拒絕美國海軍「黃蜂號」兩棲攻擊艦（USS Wasp）訪問香港，美國海軍則指出，黃蜂號近日已經轉往印大地區執行任務，期間過南海時，則進行兩棲特遣部隊防衞演習，以應對在南海「可能發生的任何軍事衝突」。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍的新聞稿指出，黃蜂號與艦上的海軍陸戰隊第31遠征部隊，正在印太地區執行任務，提高與夥伴國的聯合作戰能力，並隨時準備好應對任何安全緊急狀況。而在駛經南海海域期間，黃蜂號進行兩棲特遣部隊（DATF）綜合防禦演習，艦上水手和海軍陸戰隊員模擬穿過危險海域，向充氣目標展開實彈射擊，並進行自我防衞的演練。<br />\n<br />\n對於黃蜂號在南海演習，中國國防部發言人任國強批評美國和其他國家打着「航行自由的幌子」，違法挑釁中國主權，解放軍將加大海空巡邏警戒力度，堅定保衞領土主權和國家安全。<br />\n黃蜂號原訂下月10日訪港，中方未有透露拒絕其訪港申請的原因，中國外交部發言人耿爽曾表示，美國軍艦訪港，中方一直根據主權原則和具體情況，逐案進行審批。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180930/large/1538281695_a94b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180930%2Flarge%2F1538281695_a94b.jpg&h=10393cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海軍陸戰隊攻擊在海上的充氣目標。"},{"pid":"31e53bf6b6229c54c61fa6eb5123dff2b9865c82","tid":842281,"uid":38194,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"大巴大巴車落支那玻璃心度"},{"pid":"c7472775cfdbdd7a84be7f6789738277fe5e1dab","tid":842281,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b16a3b8061bc1637a446bb85b892a8889e20caa4","tid":842281,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"好型呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11c7de06c8c947ddff86f6d5d05734a667cfb6c","tid":842281,"uid":75326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:46:46.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;If it was 20 years ago and they had not militarized those features there, it would have just been another <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>assault ship</strong></span> on the way to Diego Garcia or whatever,&rdquo; Mattis said.<br />\n又要講多次，換隻字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0b52f76a99cd325f8169c10585b0a6f6aea1aa","tid":842281,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"行台海正啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b5e83a3112f750476457d230d0a7fef1a1edf3","tid":842281,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78079f694357313980a44804a776efe2ae5b4331","tid":842281,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"上面有冇F35B？"},{"pid":"abb7dce1f3278e85e8c9417d4b1c39e49e2a234b","tid":842281,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31e53bf6b6229c54c61fa6eb5123dff2b9865c82","tid":842281,"uid":38194,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"大巴大巴車落支那玻璃心度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec333a4b696f0ba8cefaeb83d8eb1776ba5df2e1","tid":842281,"uid":70964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37d690ac9abfd5fd0cf3c5463c6ef108d40e5661","tid":842281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180930/large/1538281695_7613.jpg\" data-t